```lisp
[
  '(:action choose ; Choose a resource and update its status
    :parameters (?entity - agent ?resource - resource)
    :precondition (and (available ?resource))
    :effect (and (chosen ?entity ?resource) (not (available ?resource)))',
  
  '(:action move
    :parameters (?agent - agent ?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (and (at ?agent ?from) (not (at ?agent ?to)))
    :effect (and (at ?agent ?to) (not (at ?agent ?from)))'
]
```
